<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idb8256bd0-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1981—<ref href="/us/pl/97/35">Pub. L. 97–35</ref> renumbered <ref href="/us/usc/t5/s3596">section 3596 of this title</ref> as this section.</p>
